Ready state maps to OCI AVAILABLE.
Requeue continues while OCI reports
PROVISIONING, the defensive literal UPDATING,
TERMINATING, or TERMINATED.
Delete completes only after GetSecurityList
returns not found; TERMINATING and TERMINATED
are accepted observed pre-delete states.
